# Copy to .dev.vars for local dev (`vite dev`). .dev.vars is gitignored.
# In production these are set as encrypted secrets via `wrangler secret put` —
# see wrangler.jsonc.

# Shared trip passcode — anyone with this can view/enter scores.
PASSCODE="changeme"

# Admin passcode — unlocks handicaps, settings, and Book commish actions.
ADMIN_PASSCODE="changeme-admin"
